    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/cbefece28cc0cc303035dc375ac82004.avif?t=1761223588\" width=1530 height=378 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现实世界已然支离破碎，你会选择在虚拟世界里现世安稳、岁月静好——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还是不惜一切地回去，直面现实、放手一搏？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家交流群：615707723（群文件有攻略和角色表情包） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bilibili：海马游戏屋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>如果您是只想游玩卡牌部分的玩家，决定完全跳过AVG部分，可以在游戏标题画面点击&quot;长明火计划&quot;图标5次，直接解锁《招式对决》模块全部内容。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/f97dde860aa4a4139295f85674636e76.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >期末考试后，军校学生雨人回到家中。和往年一样，迎接他的是朋友、青梅与妹妹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但这一次，一行人其乐融融过暑假的同时，不少异常之事正在暗中发酵。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断重复的怪梦……偶然遇见的神秘少女……边境的偷渡者……日渐紧张的政治氛围……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战争的阴霾之下，寻常与不寻常交织在几个人身边。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >终于，温馨的暑假时光被彻底打碎。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >迷雾之中的真相、突如其来的战争，一切都来得太过猛烈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >七年前究竟都发生过什么？三个国家之间有着怎样的理念差异？战争，到底因何而起？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要想知晓这些，就必须行动起来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守墓人，长明火计划，云，实验室……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这群年轻人在了解一切真相之后，会做出何种选择；能否成功，又会付出怎样的代价？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/5c57fd088cca2a8183fde1463ec9a90e.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们只做「对得起自己的作品」，因此《长明火计划》拥有——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 历时7年、15次大修的40万字科幻冒险故事，50位角色共同上演时代群像剧</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 100张CG&amp;BG（不含差分）、150种画面特效与1500段音效共同保障的游玩代入感</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 由闲踏梧桐执导的全角色配音，29位配音演员倾情献声</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 33首风格各异的BGM，绝美女声演唱的OP与ED</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 精心设计的另类卡牌闯关玩法，数十关BOSS战+高难模式充满挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 独立Rougelite地下城模式，300种各异招式带来无限可能性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 买断制游戏全程无氪金，抽卡只需游戏内金币，尽情抽到爽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >★ 丰富的附赠内容，《大将军诗集》、番外篇故事等内容更会持续免费更新</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/4d2e02401ee0c5aaad7f6d1cbd10b3bd.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/d02b835e444b4ae8291f76e3f33cf2cb.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=312 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/96e7fce86a81a230e39b2b5877bb4c86.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=301 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/7d8cf8787f0c56fc13e39fb46396695b.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=329 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/198e6df070a6c009c800abbfd354470e.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=322 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/5c0ce2fa1754a0d52d23ce410d837442.avif?t=1761223588\" width=552 height=371 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/54f425db1f34de13d3750a07ed18147c.avif?t=1761223588\" width=568 height=307 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/965a0b3c7f3350638dd87e13a4ea2b02.avif?t=1761223588\" width=554 height=308 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/383fe120f15a418e0e06e527dc77e33c.webp?t=1761223588\" width=208 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/18ff6e7cee567ab54dbbae4aaf03f12f.avif?t=1761223588\" width=500 height=1237 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1653050/extras/c3c143821161a20e8f9ff32100dd5a5a.webp?t=1761223588\" width=207 height=37 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >英雄还是懦夫，也许就在一念之间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >家国情怀、世间道义、人性光辉，当这些和生死被放在天平两端时，大多数人都会选择后者。但也有人咬咬牙，踏上了舍生取义的不归路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >史书不会记载这些默默无闻的英雄，但每个人的心里都有一束长明之火，留给曾经的他们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >毕竟，就像无名烈士墓前的大理石上所镌刻的那样——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「你的名字无人知晓，你的功绩永世长存。」</p>",
